<h5 id="truthmakers-and-language">TRUTHMAKERS AND LANGUAGE</h5>

<p><img src="/materials/schlemmer.jpg" width="410" /></p>

<div class="maintext">

  <div class="title"> ABOUT </div>

  <p>This will be a one-day workshop on truthmakers in natural language.  It will be held at All Souls College, Oxford, on 15 July 2019, in the Wharton Room.  All are welcome, but please register <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeWXevTRM8L_-L9MTnWEzhxkRQ-AgF1sXwLCiIHiwddfNoKow/viewform?usp=pp_url">here</a>.</p>

  <div class="title"> PARTICIPANTS </div>

  <p><a href="https://www.simonaimar.com/">Simona Aimar</a></p>

  <p><a href="https://www.new.ox.ac.uk/node/1423">Beau Madison Mount</a></p>

  <p><a href="https://as.nyu.edu/content/nyu-as/as/faculty/kit-fine.html">Kit Fine</a></p>

  <p><a href="http://people.umass.edu/kratzer/">Angelika Kratzer</a></p>

  <p><a href="http://users.ox.ac.uk/~sfop0776/">Matt Mandelkern</a></p>

  <p><a href="http://danielrothschild.com/">Daniel Rothschild</a></p>

  <p><a href="https://www.asc.ox.ac.uk/person/2134">Ian Rumfitt</a></p>

